WEBVTT

00:00.031 --> 00:02.572
<i>(man) Previously on Bates Motel...</i>

00:02.573 --> 00:04.340
These are for you and your son.

00:04.770 --> 00:06.337
(Norma Louise) When Annika
died, she gave me something.

00:06.338 --> 00:07.839
(Dylan) What's on it?

00:07.840 --> 00:09.674
(Norma Louise) I don't know. It's locked.

00:09.675 --> 00:11.409
(Dylan) Some guy was
just searching the office.

00:11.410 --> 00:12.543
He said that we had
something that wasn't ours.

00:12.544 --> 00:14.278
(Norma Louise) What?

00:14.279 --> 00:15.679
I'll hide it at the farm,
then we can figure out

00:15.680 --> 00:16.747
what to do together,
but it can't stay here.

00:16.748 --> 00:19.282
- Tell me to leave!
- Caleb!

00:19.283 --> 00:21.218
Is it really like she said it was?

00:21.219 --> 00:23.954
Yeah, I just want to tell her I'm sorry.

00:23.955 --> 00:26.523
(Norman) What the hell
is going on here, Dylan?

00:26.524 --> 00:28.258
Does mom know he's here?

00:28.259 --> 00:30.227
Look, we don't want any trouble.

00:30.228 --> 00:31.599
Norman!

00:32.948 --> 00:34.831
You can't tell her, you understand me?

00:34.832 --> 00:36.498
He raped her!

00:36.499 --> 00:39.368
Everything I've built with
mom... It'll all be destroyed.

00:39.369 --> 00:40.737
You betrayed mother.

00:40.738 --> 00:42.605
And she needs to know.

00:42.606 --> 00:44.707
Norman, please!

00:48.278 --> 00:51.279
[seagulls squawking]

00:53.000 --> 00:59.074
